<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="56" type="holotype">
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="56">Holotype.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="56">PORTUGAL, Estremadura: Pinhal do Rei, 8 Jan. 1991, G. Almeida, F. Estrella, F.D. Calonge (LISU-MGA 8!)*.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="56">
The species was invalidly published by 
<bibRefCitation author="Calonge, FD" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de Sociedad Micologica de Madrid" pageId="44" pageNumber="77" pagination="109 - 113" title="Tulostomalusitanicum sp. nov. (Gasteromycetes)." volume="16" year="1992">Calonge and Almeida (1992)</bibRefCitation>
and later validated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Calonge, FD" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de Sociedad Micologica de Madrid" pageId="44" pageNumber="77" pagination="301 - 302" title="Validation and confirmation of some new taxa recently published." volume="25" year="2000">Calonge (2000)</bibRefCitation>
. ITS sequence data confirm it as a distinct species (Figure 1b).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
